  "remarks": "Member of the Rajah Solaiman Movement (Qde.128). Arrested by the Philippines authorities on 14 Mar. 2011. Review pursuant to Security Council resolution\n\n1822 (2008) was concluded on 13 May 2010. Review pursuant to Security Council resolution 2368 (2017) was concluded on 4 Dec. 2019. Review pursuant to Security Council resolution 2610 (2021) was concluded on 30 October 2023.; Listing: Resolution 1735 (2006) Listed on 4 Jun. 2008 (amended on 13 Dec. 2011, 6 Dec 2019)",
